OL,5, Children struggling with obesity should
OL,6, be treated early, including with       
OL,7, medication and surgery, according to   
OL,8, new US guidelines.                     
OL,10,FThe first guidance on childhood obesity
OL,11,Fin 15 years was released by the        
OL,12,FAmerican Academy of Paediatrics on     
OL,13,FMonday.                                
OL,15,FIn it, doctors cautioned that delaying 
OL,16,Ftreatment for obesity can lead to      
OL,17,Flifelong health problems.              
OL,19,FNearly 15 million young people in the  
OL,20,FUS are considered obese.               
